ARM GAS  C:\Users\alexc\AppData\Local\Temp\ccXQ3Q3F.s 			page 13


 454:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   These parameters have an impact on ADC scope: ADC instance.
 455:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Affects both group regular and group injected (availability
 456:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         of ADC group injected depends on STM32 series).
 457:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to corresponding unitary functions into
 458:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref ADC_LL_EF_Configuration_ADC_Instance .
 459:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The setting of these parameters by function @ref LL_ADC_Init()
 460:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is conditioned to ADC state:
 461:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC instance must be disabled.
 462:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This condition is applied to all ADC features, for efficiency
 463:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and compatibility over all STM32 series. However, the different
 464:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         features can be set under different ADC state conditions
 465:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (setting possible with ADC enabled without conversion on going,
