2111:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   Possibility to update parameters on the fly:
2112:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         This function initializes multimode parameters, following
2113:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         calls to this function can be used to reconfigure some parameters
2114:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         of structure "ADC_MultiModeTypeDef" on the fly, without resetting
2115:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         the ADCs.
2116:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         The setting of these parameters is conditioned to ADC state.
2117:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         For parameters constraints, see comments of structure
2118:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         "ADC_MultiModeTypeDef".
2119:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   To move back configuration from multimode to single mode, ADC must
2120:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         be reset (using function HAL_ADC_Init() ).
2121:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param hadc Master ADC handle
2122:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param pMultimode Structure of ADC multimode configuration
